Improve interaction with polyglossia

ADD OPTION nodiac = noshadda for language Arabic which suppresses printing of shaddas

EXPAND mappings for transliteration


wa-[`alY]  or wa-[`al_A] 
The `aïn shouldn't be considered as in the middle of the word. The sukûn isn't needed in the end.

ya_hfY or ya_hf_A
Here too, there should be no sukûn in the end.



